I would Go in client.java (if you have a 317, if u have a 508 that doesnt have client.java Im sorry…LOL) Looking for home command EG: ctrl+f and type Home command, like if it is ::home look for home, then when (and if) you find it, it will say something like:
if.Command.Equals.Ignorecase(“home”)
teletoX = 3222; //change this to Home X coordinates Leave the ;
teletoY = 3222;//Change this to Home Y coordinates like i said…leave the ;
Go in player.java and look for 3222 and make sure it says something about home…Change those to home coordinates
